title: Google\Cloud\CloudDms\V1\MigrationJob
name: MigrationJob
description:
Represents a Database Migration Service migration job object.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.clouddms.v1.MigrationJob

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

methods.name: __construct
methods.description: Constructor.

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: The name (URI) of this migration job resource, in the form of: projects/{project}/locations/{location}/instances/{instance}.

params.name: data.create_time
params.description: Output only. The timestamp when the migration job resource was created. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, accurate to nanoseconds. Example: "2014-10-02T15:01:23.045123456Z".

params.name: data.update_time
params.description: Output only. The timestamp when the migration job resource was last updated. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, accurate to nanoseconds. Example: "2014-10-02T15:01:23.045123456Z".

params.name: data.labels
params.description: The resource labels for migration job to use to annotate any related underlying resources such as Compute Engine VMs. An object containing a list of "key": "value" pairs. Example: { "name": "wrench", "mass": "1.3kg", "count": "3" }.

params.name: data.display_name
params.description: The migration job display name.

params.name: data.state
params.description: The current migration job state.

params.name: data.phase
params.description: Output only. The current migration job phase.

params.name: data.type
params.description: Required. The migration job type.

params.name: data.dump_path
params.description: The path to the dump file in Google Cloud Storage, in the format: (gs://[BUCKET_NAME]/[OBJECT_NAME]).

params.name: data.source
params.description: Required. The resource name (URI) of the source connection profile.

params.name: data.destination
params.description: Required. The resource name (URI) of the destination connection profile.

params.name: data.reverse_ssh_connectivity
params.description: The details needed to communicate to the source over Reverse SSH tunnel connectivity.

params.name: data.vpc_peering_connectivity
params.description: The details of the VPC network that the source database is located in.

params.name: data.static_ip_connectivity
params.description: static ip connectivity data (default, no additional details needed).

params.name: data.duration
params.description: Output only. The duration of the migration job (in seconds). A duration in seconds with up to nine fractional digits, terminated by 's'. Example: "3.5s".

params.name: data.error
params.description: Output only. The error details in case of state FAILED.

params.name: data.source_database
params.description: The database engine type and provider of the source.

params.name: data.destination_database
params.description: The database engine type and provider of the destination.

params.name: data.end_time
params.description: Output only. If the migration job is completed, the time when it was completed.
